AddressInfo.Title: DH BP North Charging Station
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Located in the parking lot of the BP North, at the right hand side of the buildings front.

Connections.Comments: An adjustable power output ranges from 12 - 32 amps to help you find the most efficient charge for your electric vehicle and existing wiring. The Level 2- 240V American made EV800 Series lets you choose between 12 - 32 amps of power, and can charge compatible EVs up 5 times faster than a standard 110V outlet.
